text: Mynagappally is a village in Kollam district, Kerala, India. ==Politics== The village is under the leadership of LDF Party. The Mynagappally Panchayath President is Smt P K Jayalekshmi. The Vice President is Sri.Reghunathan pillai ==Transport== Sasthamcotta railway station is in this village. ==Economy== The major jobs are regarding to cashew factories, brick manufacturing, tile manufacturing, coir industry and matchbox industry. == References == Category:Villages in Kollam district
title: Mynagappally
